FE_anaphoraPos, FE_antecedentPos, FE_distance, FE_isSubj, FE_neType, FE_pronounCountSentence, FE_sentenceOffset, FE_stringMatch
public abstract class AbstractFeatureExtractor
extends java.lang.Object

Common methods/fields for every feature extractor.
A Feature Extractor handles feature extraction and distribution in respect to a CoreferencePair.
The Feature Extractor is a unique object and adds a corresponding instance of Feature + the correct value for this feature.
